init_text: When you die, you appear in a cinema with a number of other people who look like you. You find out that they are your previous reincarnations, and soon you all begin watching your next life on the big screen.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You are all very disappointed, and you all begin to wonder why you were shown this life.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Then you are told that you were shown this life so that you would be happy with your next life.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You are then told that you will all be reincarnated again, and you are all excited to see what your next life will be like

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You could be rich or poor.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You are all then shown a vision of your next life.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You are a dog who is very happy and has a nice family.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You are very happy with your life, but you are not sure why you are a dog.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You are so happy that you are a dog, and you are so happy that you are the dog that belongs to the boy.
